@startuml
title ArcHub CMS - Content Modeling Application Service
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor "Model editor" as Editor
component "Model admin routes" as Routes
component "ArcHubModelingService\napplication.modeling" as Modeling
component "ArcHubDomainEvent" as Event
component "ArcHubCMSService\ncompatibility API" as CMS
database "SQLite CMS store" as DB
component "Package promotion" as Packages
component "Content editor" as Content

Editor --> Routes : edit data types,\ntemplates, types,\ncompositions, blueprints
Routes --> Modeling : report / upsert / delete
Modeling --> CMS : existing model methods
CMS --> DB : archub_data_types\narchub_templates\narchub_content_types\narchub_content_compositions\narchub_content_blueprints
Modeling --> Event : content_model.* events
Packages ..> Modeling : future model import\nand migration boundary
Content ..> Modeling : blueprint catalog\nand schema reports
Modeling --> Routes : compatible JSON or redirect result
@enduml
